&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Continua... &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;N&amp;atilde;o passamos esse v&amp;iacute;deo na noite de proje&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, mas achei interessante link&amp;aacute;-lo pois fala um pouco da Lei Espec&amp;iacute;fica da Billings.&lt;iframe allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; height=&quot;315&quot; src=&quot;//www.youtube.com/embed/gcPTYL-hGm8&quot; width=&quot;420&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
